videos.headline: Zia Cooke puts defender in the spin cycle for a bucket
videos.description: Zia Cooke runs the break and uses a spin move to confuse her defender and pull up to hit the transition bucket for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Zia Cooke puts defender in the spin cycle for a bucket) 2021/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aliyah Boston battles for and-1 bucket
videos.description: Aliyah Boston gets inside and fights off defenders to get the ball up and in through contact for an and-1 basket for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Aliyah Boston battles for and-1 bucket) 2021/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aliyah Boston racks up 5 blocks in win vs. NC State
videos.description: Aliyah Boston puts on a stellar defensive performance as she records five blocks in South Carolina's season-opening win on the road against NC State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Aliyah Boston racks up 5 blocks in win vs. NC State) 2021/11/09 ESHEET Sotfull
